Aida Kamel (1931 - September 7, 2020) bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri.
Ọ gụrụ redio na mahadum wee nweta nzere bachelọ
Ọ na-arụ ọrụ na ihe nkiri kemgbe mmalite afọ 1950
N'etiti ihe nkiri ya bụ: Sit El Hassan, The Melody of Eternity, Always With You, The empty pillow, Ismail Yiss na Al-Tayaran, Alexandria..
N'ihi gịnị?. Kemgbe afọ 1980s, ọ sonyekwara na ihe nkiri telivishọn dị ka Bein Kasserine, The Judiciary in Islam na Huanem Garden City.
Kamel nwụrụ n'ụlọ ọgwụ dị na Cairo na 7 Septemba 2020 mgbe ọ dị afọ iri asatọ na itoolu, mgbe ọ rịasịrị ọrịa ogologo oge.
